                        </cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> accurate cognoscens </quote>
                        </cit>: episcopus sit <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢነሣኤ፡ ገጽ፤ መበይን፤ ዘኢያደሉ፡ ለባዕል፡ ወኢለነዳይ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Did." loc="4 ">Did. 4 </ref>(<ref cRef="Platt p." loc="18">Platt p. 18</ref>). </sense>
               
            <sense xml:lang="en" source="#traces" xml:id="Tmain"> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez">
                            <quote> mabayyǝn </quote>
                        </cit> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ ኖኅ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ወከመ፡ ሙሴ፡ የዋህ፡ ከመ፡ ዳንኤል፡ መበይን፡</foreign> ‘<cit type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                            <quote> A Noè il giusto (Sir 44, 17), oppure a Mosè il mite (Sir 45, 4), a Daniele che discerne </quote>
                        </cit>’ <bibl>
